description: Mutts Amazing Dogs is Oklahoma City's premier joint for tasty 100% beef kosher franks and chicken dogs! Vegetarian? They've also got a veggie-friendly falafel dog! Gluten free buns are also available for $2.50. Make sure to grab one of their many tasty sides to complement your meal, like their deviled eggs, red skinned potato salad, baked beans or of course some crispy fries (regular or add truffle oil).
name: Mutts Amazing Dogs
